<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>College Cleaners</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/cleaners.css">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body ng-app="Cleaners">
	<!-- top nav bar -->
	<nav class="navbar navbar-default">
		<div class="container-fluid">
			<div class="navbar-header">
				<a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<p class="navbar-text right">Signed in as <a href="#" class="navbar-link">Jack Mulrow</a></p>
		</div>
	</nav>
	<!-- end nav bar -->
	<!-- everything else -->
	<div class="container">

		<div class="row">
			<!-- left sidebar -->
			<div
			class="sidebar col-sm-4 col-xs-12"
			ng-controller="SidebarCtrl">
				<div class="list-group" ng-repeat="request in requests">
					<request request="request" ng-click="setSelected(request)"></request>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- main stuff -->
			<div class="main-content col-sm-8 col-xs-12" ng-controller="MainCtrl">
				<div class="place-holder" ng-hide="selected.request">
					<h2>Select a request from the sidebar</h2>
					<p>
						Vestibulum imperdiet leo ut congue auctor. Donec imperdiet mi sit amet nibh suscipit tincidunt. Morbi eleifend posuere euismod. Fusce tempus diam purus, a ultrices purus consequat nec. Vestibulum mollis quis quam in faucibus. Nam vel mi neque. Vivamus eleifend erat sed urna blandit tincidunt. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Nunc eget fringilla ante. Donec eget gravida massa. Aenean a purus sit amet felis iaculis luctus. Duis ut lectus a ligula cursus pharetra vehicula sit amet mauris. Pellentesque egestas, quam vel varius facilisis, quam augue varius tellus, eu maximus quam lorem tristique lorem. Nam eget orci nibh. Etiam a augue neque. Aliquam et sem magna.
					</p>
				</div>
				<!-- specific request -->
				<active-request ng-show="selected.request" request="selected.request"></active-request>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
<!-- angular stuff -->
<script src="angular/angular.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/app-cleaners.js"></script>
<script src="js/controllers/MainCtrl.js"></script>
<script src="js/controllers/SidebarCtrl.js"></script>
<script src="js/directives/request/request.js"></script>
<script src="js/directives/activeRequest/activeRequest.js"></script>
<script src="js/factories/RequestsFactory.js"></script>
<script src="js/factories/SelectedFactory.js"></script>

<!-- everything else -->
<script src="js/main.js"></script>
</html>